Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.56,0:00:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切开始于神木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.66,0:00:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断战斗\N不断祈求  不断寻找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.63,0:00:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从中产生了强烈的羁绊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.47,0:00:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全新的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.47,0:00:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光明的未来从现在开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.71,0:00:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与奈落的战斗结束后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.37,0:00:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本关系\N应该更加和谐的两个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.51,0:00:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却由于弥勒法师的缘故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.91,0:00:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人的关系出现了裂痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.51,0:00:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子真的好吗  珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.78,0:00:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引导我们的最后一块碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.52,0:00:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枯井的另一边\N战国的世界里还有明天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.95,0:00:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战国时代的传说故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.15,0:00:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.29,0:00:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为谁而流的眼泪祈祷般地流下脸颊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.40,0:00:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要隐藏脆弱  温柔地接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.04,0:00:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连呼吸都忘记  眼中的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.18,0:00:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有太阳闪耀着 不断寻找着什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.08,0:01:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凝视镜子 你一定能看见立誓的那天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.86,0:01:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的背后也有翅膀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.97,0:01:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的改变  将改变世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.74,0:01:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实现梦想的爱的火焰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.17,0:01:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿越虚幻的海市蜃楼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.52,0:01:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空有光  大地有水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.45,0:01:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚强的心灵带你到未来的ANGELUS（奉告祈祷）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.20,0:01:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双手握紧热情的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.15,0:02:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师还在沮丧耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.52,0:02:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为被扒手扒走了钱包吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.52,0:02:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  都是我的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.69,0:02:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.53,0:02:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别这么沮丧了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.70,0:02:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.13,0:02:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要对我说\N这么贴心的话好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.10,0:02:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.74,0:02:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我实在没有办法原谅自己\N这么粗心犯下的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.58,0:02:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.68,0:02:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是沮丧的表现吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.82,0:02:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的和做的完全两回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.52,0:02:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第161话\N弥勒法师的陈年旧帐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.36,0:02:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是向得道高僧求来的灵符
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.43,0:02:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个的话一定能够镇得住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.44,0:03:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地震
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.18,0:03:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.04,0:03:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有妖气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.48,0:03:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.75,0:03:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.42,0:03:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您原谅啊  湖神大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.62,0:03:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.76,0:03:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来好像是\N为了什么怪异的事情在烦恼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.13,0:03:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果您不介意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.46,0:03:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们愿意助您一臂之力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.43,0:03:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥…弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.23,0:03:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.07,0:03:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您真的要按照约定\N入赘到我们家吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.11,0:03:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入赘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.78,0:03:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.58,0:03:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点准备招待法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.62,0:03:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.08,0:03:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.42,0:03:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想不起来了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.96,0:03:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说同样的事\N要想起来会太多了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.46,0:03:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.66,0:03:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等您回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.64,0:04:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志麻姑娘\N你真是越来越美了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.47,0:04:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高兴喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.51,0:04:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.02,0:04:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是过去的事了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.02,0:04:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.69,0:04:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们夫妻\N本来也以为这件事已经过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.02,0:04:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算放弃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.02,0:04:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的女儿志麻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.32,0:04:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自幼就是体弱多病的体质
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.76,0:04:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能过着终日卧床不起的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.03,0:04:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候弥勒法师\N正好路过我们这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.60,0:04:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那已经是两年前的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.40,0:04:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请将这种药草以清水煎煮后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.04,0:04:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天服用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.47,0:04:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是昂贵的药草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.91,0:04:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疗效果然非凡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.85,0:04:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是非常昂贵的药草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.62,0:04:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又坑了别人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.12,0:04:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来\N两个人的感情越来越好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.86,0:04:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.92,0:04:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师给了我们药草之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.23,0:04:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就匆匆离去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.63,0:05:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.80,0:05:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是清白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.20,0:05:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.57,0:05:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.23,0:05:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你康复之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.50,0:05:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以为我生孩子吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.74,0:05:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.01,0:05:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵重的药草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.71,0:05:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及分别时\N跟弥勒法师之间的约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.01,0:05:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为我心灵的支柱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.95,0:05:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来我果然彻底康复了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.38,0:05:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然又是在追求人家嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.15,0:05:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好啊  反正都是过去的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.76,0:05:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  无聊死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.76,0:05:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情怎样都无所谓吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.96,0:05:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.53,0:05:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是刚才说的怪异的事\N是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.23,0:05:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.40,0:05:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才在祠堂那边发生的事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.90,0:05:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有地震耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.91,0:05:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好怕喔  弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.54,0:05:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我害怕的是另外一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.68,0:05:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师\N请您一定要救救我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.12,0:05:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这么下去\N女儿就要成为妖怪的新娘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.62,0:06:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为妖怪的新娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.06,0:06:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.69,0:06:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那座祠堂\N是用来祭祀湖神大人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.93,0:06:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个湖神大人说\N无论如何一定要志麻嫁给他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.63,0:06:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也跟他说\N我已经有了未婚夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.00,0:06:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他就是不相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.81,0:06:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问  未婚夫是指…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.77,0:06:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是指你吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.51,0:06:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是弥勒法师并没有忘记\N跟我的约定而回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.88,0:06:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是多么期盼着\N这一天的到来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.46,0:06:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.09,0:06:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.03,0:06:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能把志麻姑娘\N交给那个妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.46,0:06:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您愿意帮助我们吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.30,0:06:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事就交给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.40,0:06:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么马上举办婚礼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.67,0:06:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不是要我们把妖怪除掉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.24,0:06:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来对方不论怎样\N都想生下弥勒的孩子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.82,0:07:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志麻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.75,0:07:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚上就是约定的日子咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.07,0:07:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.20,0:07:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么只有弥勒留在房子里面呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.01,0:07:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.14,0:07:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像说有事要商量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.51,0:07:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒绝当入赘的女婿吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.01,0:07:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.88,0:07:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为弥勒法师\N已经跟珊瑚订下婚约了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.39,0:07:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以相信那个家伙吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.72,0:07:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是弥勒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.36,0:07:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送到嘴边不吃是男人的耻辱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.66,0:07:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  你给我坐下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.03,0:07:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么时候\N学会说这种坏话的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.60,0:07:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且要说也要顺便看看场合啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.04,0:07:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.48,0:08:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很希望\N您能够尽早和我女儿完婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.81,0:08:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是想抢走志麻姑娘的湖神大人\N是妖怪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.48,0:08:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管志麻姑娘\N是否嫁给他人为妻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.19,0:08:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也都会来抢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.92,0:08:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算举办婚礼也没用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.92,0:08:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  正是时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.93,0:08:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湖神大人说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.39,0:08:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要一个清纯的少女\N来当他的新娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.33,0:08:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  如果举行了婚礼的话\N他就不得不放弃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.50,0:08:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他这么重礼教啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.64,0:08:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么样\N在湖神大人来这里之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.64,0:08:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我成为弥勒法师的妻子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.61,0:08:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志麻姑娘…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.11,0:08:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不接受女人的求爱\N可是男人的耻辱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.91,0:08:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.92,0:08:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥…勒…法…师…\N怪…怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.69,0:08:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宝  你在干什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.29,0:08:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是试着把珊瑚的心情\N表现出来而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.49,0:08:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有生气呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.30,0:08:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  打扰你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.64,0:09:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧  混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.44,0:09:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的眼睛好像是在说\N“去死吧  混蛋”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.54,0:09:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.45,0:09:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位女客人是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.55,0:09:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  不瞒您说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.05,0:09:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有地震
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.05,0:09:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是个\N带着腥味的家伙接近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.66,0:09:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照这么看起来  好像是那个\N叫什么湖神大人的驾临了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.24,0:09:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是湖神大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.71,0:09:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依照约定\N我来迎娶志麻姑娘为我的妻子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.48,0:09:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然他这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.84,0:09:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个家伙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.45,0:09:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已经自报姓名了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.32,0:09:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.86,0:09:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要来阻碍我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.49,0:09:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家那位姑娘不愿意啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.40,0:10:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湖…湖神大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.10,0:10:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师  好可怕喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.10,0:10:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有那么可怕吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.87,0:10:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志麻姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.37,0:10:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.27,0:10:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  死心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.14,0:10:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.74,0:10:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是已经清清楚楚约定好\N要嫁给我了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.71,0:10:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约定好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.01,0:10:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有跟你约定好什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.29,0:10:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您原谅我  湖神大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.62,0:10:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.99,0:10:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.09,0:10:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为要煎煮那么贵重的药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.89,0:10:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请将这种药草以清水煎煮后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.50,0:10:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天服用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.40,0:10:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是用湖中的水来煎煮药的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.90,0:10:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且因为顺路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.90,0:10:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我每天都到湖的祠堂许下愿望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.24,0:10:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湖神大人啊\N请治好我女儿的身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.14,0:10:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管您要我们\N怎么报答您都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.78,0:10:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作梦也没想到这些话\N真的被湖神大人听见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.45,0:11:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此湖神大人说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.66,0:11:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让志麻姑娘嫁给他\N以作为报答吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.19,0:11:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说这件事会是我的错吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.89,0:11:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么觉得他有点可怜耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.30,0:11:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.40,0:11:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲竟然许下了那样的约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.67,0:11:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志麻  对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.47,0:11:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.47,0:11:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为您一心一意\N盼着我的病能够治得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.18,0:11:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.58,0:11:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是没办法的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.55,0:11:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然说我事先不知情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.05,0:11:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是约定就是约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.48,0:11:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也就是说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.58,0:11:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志麻姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.69,0:11:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会\N真的要嫁给这个妖怪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.46,0:11:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湖神大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.43,0:11:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.96,0:11:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本就没有\N成为湖神大人新娘的资格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.17,0:11:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.94,0:11:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.84,0:11:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湖神大人您希望\N娶一个清纯的少女作为新娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.81,0:11:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我已经在两年前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.85,0:12:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟这位弥勒法师结合为夫妇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.08,0:12:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的是这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.85,0:12:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志麻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.62,0:12:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  父亲大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.52,0:12:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事我实在无法说出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.72,0:12:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早料到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.36,0:12:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就算改口这样说\N还是觉得很震惊耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.86,0:12:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好啊  已经是过去的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.00,0:12:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湖神大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.00,0:12:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么一回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.14,0:12:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您当作没有发生过这件事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.24,0:12:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们欺骗了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.62,0:12:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓爱越深恨越深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.02,0:12:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大鲶鱼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.86,0:12:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要让你们这些家伙\N体会我的悲伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.40,0:12:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的房子就快要被毁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.53,0:12:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师  救救我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.77,0:12:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了  让我们来镇住它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.27,0:12:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们上  珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.94,0:13:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人去收拾吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.64,0:13:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是你以前犯的错吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.58,0:13:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…请问…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.38,0:13:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位女客人\N她也要开始变身了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.02,0:13:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…她不是妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.82,0:13:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是争论的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.96,0:13:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的房子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.53,0:13:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的对手是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.97,0:13:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要一口把你吃掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.20,0:13:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚  听我说你就明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.07,0:13:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离我远一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.11,0:13:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我们果然是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.58,0:13:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.28,0:13:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个人会变得怎么样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.35,0:13:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.29,0:13:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在应该是要看\N犬夜叉跟大鲶鱼那边吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.23,0:13:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢把我当傻瓜一样耍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.97,0:14:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少自大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.84,0:14:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.44,0:14:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想打的话  我可是不会留情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.65,0:14:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志麻姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.12,0:14:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来是这么的相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.09,0:14:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他镇静下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.02,0:14:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湖神大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.99,0:14:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在是不是已经对我死心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.60,0:14:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就没有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.97,0:14:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  就算杀了这个家伙\N也会睡得不安稳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.67,0:14:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  那边的事态\N好像越来越严重了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.38,0:14:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  还在吵啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.25,0:14:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.65,0:14:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你连我的话都不想听了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.92,0:14:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.15,0:14:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不想管了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.99,0:14:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.62,0:14:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个弥勒花心又好色的毛病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.66,0:15:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是从今天昨天才开始的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.16,0:15:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.63,0:15:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.53,0:15:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你真的一点都不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.40,0:15:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果过去曾经\N跟对方交往过的女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.27,0:15:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现在自己的面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.80,0:15:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情怎么可能会好嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.27,0:15:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个  请你们不要吵架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.41,0:15:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志麻姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.38,0:15:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切都是我不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.78,0:15:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你不要责怪弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.95,0:15:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.95,0:15:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.02,0:15:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师  你不追吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.56,0:15:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不管我说什么\N她都听不进去了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.10,0:15:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是感觉真的有一些落寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.97,0:15:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到\N她竟然对我如此不信任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.21,0:15:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明我的心\N一直都属于她一个人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.34,0:15:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听起来好像是在说\N他是冤枉的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.11,0:15:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的是冤枉的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.49,0:15:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志麻\N救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.85,0:16:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是喜欢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.32,0:16:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.46,0:16:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您放过我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.13,0:16:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.13,0:16:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起在湖底生活吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.26,0:16:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶\N果然应该给它最后致命的一击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.63,0:16:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧去追人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.22,0:16:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师没有追来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.79,0:16:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后我该怎么办呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.90,0:16:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊\N不管发生什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.03,0:16:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都要成为我的新娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.73,0:16:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说过\N我已经跟弥勒法师结合了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.97,0:16:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会原谅你的\N我可以原谅你过去的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.01,0:16:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.76,0:17:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是弥勒法师的同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.43,0:17:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.93,0:17:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.83,0:17:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他根本就不是来追我的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.11,0:17:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.98,0:17:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个人带到安全的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.68,0:17:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞来骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.21,0:17:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太愚蠢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.28,0:17:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞来骨被弹开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.97,0:17:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.47,0:17:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看我就顺便把你带到湖底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.74,0:17:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我的小妾吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.31,0:18:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.21,0:18:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.52,0:18:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然敢抓我的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.25,0:18:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.49,0:18:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里可是湖水之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.73,0:18:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可能\N会被你这个家伙抓住呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.50,0:18:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.94,0:18:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此  这招怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.57,0:18:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.96,0:18:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水好像…开始消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.57,0:19:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.89,0:19:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个臭鲶鱼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.59,0:19:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我警告你  不准动我的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.86,0:19:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个女人也是你的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.26,0:19:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.00,0:19:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚  你没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.01,0:19:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.48,0:19:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.59,0:19:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.92,0:19:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在叫你呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.86,0:19:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.83,0:20:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚  等等我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.06,0:20:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然没有…我上场的机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.40,0:20:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.34,0:20:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到头来\N这只是一段无法实现的恋情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.68,0:20:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我说谎欺骗了大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.95,0:20:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟弥勒法师已经结合的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.02,0:20:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是假的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.19,0:20:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.12,0:20:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我不想当鲶鱼的新娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.63,0:20:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不知不觉就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.19,0:20:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想这也可以说\N是志麻姑娘急中生智吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.56,0:20:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如…如果是那样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.40,0:20:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把这个真相\N告诉我一个人不就好了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.47,0:20:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.87,0:20:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我对你非常的信任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.98,0:20:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为不说出来你也会明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.21,0:20:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.11,0:20:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来这都要怪我\N平日行为不端吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.42,0:20:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你留下了不好的回忆\N真是对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.89,0:21:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.32,0:21:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.79,0:21:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.16,0:21:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你救我的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.20,0:21:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是觉得有点高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.60,0:21:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你原谅我了吗  珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.97,0:21:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这句话应该是我要说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.07,0:21:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.41,0:21:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚的心胸真的好宽大喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.98,0:21:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者应该说比戈薇宽大吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.25,0:21:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们很相配呢  弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.43,0:21:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.46,0:21:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是早点否认的话\N就不会发生那种事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.40,0:21:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说  弥勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.60,0:21:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会是\N为了要回想起过去的记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.17,0:21:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花了很长的时间吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.97,0:21:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说中了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.14,0:21:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那样的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.28,0:21:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说  是那样的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.15,0:22:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正都是过去的事了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.35,0:22:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brand-New World 全新梦想的起点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.36,0:22:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝向目标持续旅程 直到最后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.30,0:22:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brand-New Mind 怀抱热情直到下一扇门扉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.58,0:22:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲向未知的世界 快奔驰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.09,0:22:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸手触摸 那微尘般的希望之星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.82,0:22:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使勉强握住 横冲直撞的我们想往何处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.60,0:22:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保有自我 Let's go and Try 前进吧 使命只有One way
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.67,0:23:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺其自然 Do it!Ready? 最后愿望将达成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.85,0:23:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brand-New World 全新梦想的起点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.82,0:23:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝向目标持续旅程 直到最后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.93,0:23:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brand-New Mind 怀抱热情直到下一扇门扉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.14,0:23:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲向未知的世界 快奔驰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.99,0:23:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  邪见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.63,0:23:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小玲被妖怪抓走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.66,0:23:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专门驱魔除妖的法师\N好像已经去救她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.30,0:23:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那位法师平生最恨妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.23,0:23:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是他和杀生丸碰上\N事情就不妙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.47,0:23:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类那种不成气候的法术\N能有什么用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.74,0:23:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对会被杀生丸撕成碎片的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.84,0:23:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点都不害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.58,0:24:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.04,0:24:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远与杀生丸少爷在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.61,0:24:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.01,0:24:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算小玲死了\N请您也不要忘记我



